items.text: The pork chop at the front are super tender.

Red stove hokkien mee is nice
have dinner over there !
Western food #01-2821 红美西餐... Must try !!
BEST WESTERN FOOD In this market . Its a must try. :)
Mui Kee fish ball noodles. Good noodles at great price.
Cheap and good desert store. Ice kachang only $1.20
Wanton mee is nice at 01-2867!! Nice dumplings as well! Very crunchy! 兴记云吞面!! Must try the dumplings!!!
甜品之家 for some really healthy and delicous 八宝豆花/八宝仙草! +++  highly recommend. Reasonable price and healthy dessert!
Kampong BBQ
Under renovation till December 2017
Lovin' the bbq stingray near Fairprice ;D
Bak chor mee: Bendemeer Mushroom Minced Meat Noodle #01-2741 is unexpectedly tasty! Right mix of sauce, although my fried wantans were 'lao hong' (turned soft)
Vegetarian options: Ala carte @Vegetarian Inn #01-2877, rojak, local pancake, fried carrot cake, soya beancurd, fruits, vegetarian beehoon, yong tau foo, yu tiao (dough fritters), popiah, soon kueh
Popular hot n cold dessert here
Mee rebus. Enjoyed my plate from Suhaime's #01-2879 (corner stall in centre). Sauce was thick, sweet w occasional bite of dried shrimp. They claim on their sign that recipe's of Geylang Lor 1 fame
The nasi lemak store was heard to be relocating to blk 57 (the coffeeshop opp MSCP)... 3 cheers for good breakfast!
The bread her is superp!!!!!!
Suppose to be blk 69 not 3200...
Try the bread stall's bread!! Fresh from the oven!!
Try Blk 68 Nasi Lemak.. Cheap & Nice.. But sold out super fast every morning!
Try the chicken rice stall that's next to the braised duck rice. The set is only $3.50

Duck rice: $3 buys u this. Duck meat yummy, w starchy-style sauce. Enjoyed it their punchy sour chilli sauce. Soup appeared diluted, altho can still taste herbs. Didn't taste any yam @ all in rice :-(
is gg hm from my stall shag
western food stalls weren't that good...
Fishball noodles. Get yourself an honest bowl of Teochew fishball noodles fr Mui Kee #01-2817. Simple & fragrant. Comes with 'he kiao' (fish dumplings) & fish cake slices
Farrer Road Fish Soup can give it a try
Soto at Warung Hj Morsode. Fuyooo......
Love Hiap Heng Kee Hainese Chicken Rice - rice is not too oily, nice bite my favorite
Love the western food with the red signboard!!
So many 'empty' but no table!!!!
Newly opened stall 69 Cold Soya Beancurb - it's very nice n smooth comes in different flavors Almond, Green Tea, Durian or normal Soya BeanCurb worth the try
cheap and tasty mee soto and satay
There are alot of nice foods here, cheok kee boneless braised, hock ann noodle, sheng kee cook food n many more
I strongly agreed but very stuffy inside
curry fish head ! just $8.00
favorite since secondary school western food 
Jing ji xiao chi tan #01-2855 has nice porridge beehoon n chee cheong fun but be early. Come after 9am and it's closed. Best to b here at 6-7am (:
Wantan mee: WTM prepared by Shi De Fu #01-2835 was salty; char siew slices bland. While  wantans hv nice ingredients like chopped water chestnut, the whole dish was average. Order if u r not fussy
Carpark. If carpark right in front of mkt/food ctr is full, plenty more lots just ard corner, behind Blk 68
New R R corner Must try Nasir lemak!!!
Hong Mei Western Delights #01-2821 Open after five, be prepared to wait.
bread stalls, hock ann, shi de fu, red stove fried noodle, shen lee soya bean, 經濟小吃摊, 水粿罗卜糕, sheng kee cooked food, mui kee fish noodle, hong mei western n lian huat drink stall all more than 25yrs

My go-to local coffee. My kopi was very smooth & fragrant; none of that musty coffee sachet smell. Honest recommendation by another food stall when I asked who brewed the best kopi in this food centre
Dabao-ed home the black carrot cake and it still tasted so good!
Nice Yong tau foo at the corner stall of this food center
Nice big chunky fried carrot cake here
Sheng kee cooked food selling soya sauce chicken noodle is heaven! Must try!
Soya sauce chicken noodle. Compared to Chiew Kee along Upp Cross St, dish fr Sheng Kee #01-2795 is not as mouth-watering. But portion is generous. Wantan mee is also above ave (served w shuigao!)
great wonton & chicken noodles here!
Sheng Kee Cooked Food has the best Chicken Noodles!
Most stalls increased price ..... :(
Ma Bo lor me value for money and taste great. Fried fish made fresh this very crunchy.
Curry chicken noodles are nice !
Try the minced pork noodle here. And ask for extra mushrooms and that crispy pork thing.
Ordered half chicken + bean sprouts & a plate of drumstickss. Only $10. Where can get so cheap & yummy de sia? O.O
Try the "Sarawak Kolo Mee" Really best in town! 卧虎藏龙
Wahahaha. Both sisters married to the same man! Common in the olden days. Seriously, their food is good considered to many places.
Tan Kee's Roasted from mains to the chili to the big bowl of free soup. Slurpy to the last drop.
Lotsa good food here
Heng loong coffee nice close on friday.
Noodles cottage de mee hoon kway power!!
Hwa Kee Yong Tau Foo is a must try!
@ Lexelle d. -- what thing scandalous? Share leh...
Hey everyone try the 回味板面 it is very nice ....yummy eating it for dinner now :)))))
You have go try the duck rice and the soft puffy buns!!
Hock Ann is always my fave stalls and I love the carrot cake beside red stove
Wantan mee: When ordering WTM fr Hock Ann #01-2833, note that the jovial stallholder serves just wantans. No vege, no char siew (BBQ pork) slices. Simple comfort meal :-)
Kampong BBQ #01-2765, indonesian cuisine.

Welcome to Heng Huat Chicken & Duck Rice (block 69 #01-2765) our Roasted chicken is different from others and it's not dip fried in oil. We also provide Delivery Service do contact SAM at 84485951 for
广东砂煲饭.盅仔饭.燉汤 #01-2785
BBQ Fish Rice. Not bad.
I love the carrot cake from the man with two wives!
Take - A - Bite bubble tea is awesome!
Have Birthday Dinner With Uncle At Nite !
Once it operates, it's hell's kitchen; so hot and stuffy that you can die a million times before you finish eating!
Try the soon kueh here!
DIY popiah: Fortune Food #01-2777 sells handmade (actually central kitchen) Popiah skin ($15/kg), ground peanuts, crispy bits, chilli sauce, etc to host ur own Popiah party @ home. Nice.
There's a new that sells beancurd! Must try! #01-2763
Bee Kee carrot cake is quite nice, above average I'd say...
Eggs & French toasts for breakfast? Track down Chinese-signed stall 古苓精怪麵包 (Gu Lin Jing Guai Mian Bao) #01-2837. Eggs (fried or sunny-side up), ham or luncheon meat slices, pork sausages. Unique meal
the Pu Tien food stall is excellent.
Guan Hin homemade carrot cake and fried kway grow is good.
Try Cheok Kee Boneless Braised Duck.
红美西餐. Best! My regular anti-depressant. Get item 10A, fish and chicken. Lovely.
Vegetarian zichar. Vegetarian Inn #01-2877 prepares ala carte items after u order. Interesting non-meat local faves like laksa, fried Hokkien mee, sliced fish bee hoon, mee goreng & even kway chap!
Scheduled for renovation from October 2016 for 10 months, come eat your fill before they move and disappear!
